description:
On today’s show, Emily is talking about the importance of self care & why we must put ourselves first instead of the ones around us. Plus, she’s answering your sex related questions. 

She discusses why it’s so hard to develop new & healthier habits for ourselves, what to do when you feel “off” after masturbating but not after sex, & how to properly exercise your dating muscles. 


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com
